rows.name:
I wonder if the Holy See's goddess
is a goddess of money?

rows.label: tlk41100171_02_msg0002
rows.name:
Tourists toss coins from Milama Viewpoint
into the Cloud Sea, but a lot of them
land over here.

rows.label: tlk41100171_02_msg0003
rows.name:
Thanks to the funeral, more coins than
usual are raining down. It must be thanks
to the goddess.
